<figureCitation box="[159,232,1014,1039]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1967,1989]" captionTargetBox="[160,1427,208,1929]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[152,1435,193,1945]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Habitus of Liogluta. A, L. changwhani sp. nov.; B, L. distans; C, L. granigera; D, L. infans. E, L. jinilli sp. nov.; F, L. pyonganica; G, L. rufescens sp. nov.; H, L. ursi." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/166919/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="299">Figs. 1</figureCitation>
